{"title":"前端学习笔记（五）","uid":"9f847fa25e577b1edbe140706f5dda4e","slug":"前端学习笔记（五）","date":"2022-04-02T08:19:00.000Z","updated":"2022-04-02T16:28:53.999Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/前端学习笔记（五）.json","keywords":"C++,Pyhton,Java,算法","cover":"/img/css.jpeg","content":"<p>上一篇学习了CSS的选择器，这一篇就学习：</p>\n<h2 id=\"css属性\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#css属性\"></a> CSS属性</h2>\n<h3 id=\"字体\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#字体\"></a> 字体</h3>\n<p>使用font-family属性对元素的字体定义样式，可以设置多种不同的字体(如果浏览器不支持当前字体则找下一个字体替换)，字体之间用逗号隔开。字体名称可以是中文名，但是最好写英文名。</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-html\" data-language=\"html\"><code class=\"language-html\"><span class=\"token doctype\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;!</span><span class=\"token doctype-tag\">doctype</span> <span class=\"token name\">html</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>html</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>head</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>meta</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">charset</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>utf-8<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>title</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>字体样式<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>title</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>style</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">type</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>text/css<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token style\"><span class=\"token language-css\">\n        <span class=\"token selector\">body</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">&#123;</span>\n            <span class=\"token comment\">/* 页面基本属性 */</span>\n            <span class=\"token property\">font-family</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> Arial<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> Helvetica<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> sans-serif<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span><span class=\"token string\">\"宋体\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n            <span class=\"token comment\">/* 字体类型 */</span>\n        <span class=\"token punctuation\">&#125;</span>\n    </span></span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>style</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>head</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>body</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>p</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>定义字体类型<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>p</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>body</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>html</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre>\n<h3 id=\"字号\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#字号\"></a> 字号</h3>\n<p>使用font-size属性对元素的文字大小定义样式，常用单位是px(像素)、em(以父辈字体大小为参考值设置大小)。</p>\n<p>标题标签要单独特别指定大小。</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-html\" data-language=\"html\"><code class=\"language-html\"><span class=\"token doctype\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;!</span><span class=\"token doctype-tag\">doctype</span> <span class=\"token name\">html</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>html</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>head</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>meta</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">charset</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>utf-8<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>title</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>字体样式<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>title</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>style</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">type</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>text/css<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token style\"><span class=\"token language-css\">\n        <span class=\"token selector\">body</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">&#123;</span>\n            <span class=\"token comment\">/* 网页字体大小 */</span>\n            <span class=\"token property\">font-size</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 0.75em<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n            <span class=\"token comment\">/* 约等于12像素 */</span>\n        <span class=\"token punctuation\">&#125;</span>\n\n        <span class=\"token selector\">body,\n        div,\n        p</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">&#123;</span>\n            <span class=\"token property\">font-size</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 0.75em<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n        <span class=\"token punctuation\">&#125;</span>\n    </span></span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>style</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>head</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>body</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>div</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">id</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>content<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>框架\n        <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>div</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">id</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>sub<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>子框架\n            <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>p</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>段落文本<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>p</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n        <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>body</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>html</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre>\n<h3 id=\"字体粗细\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#字体粗细\"></a> 字体粗细</h3>\n<p>使用font-weight属性对元素的文字粗细定义样式，常用属性值有normal、bold、bolder、lighter等自带的属性值，也有数值属性值，一般normal=400。</p>\n<p>标题标签要单独特别指定粗细。</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-html\" data-language=\"html\"><code class=\"language-html\"><span class=\"token doctype\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;!</span><span class=\"token doctype-tag\">doctype</span> <span class=\"token name\">html</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>html</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>head</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>meta</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">charset</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>utf-8<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>title</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>字体样式<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>title</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>style</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">type</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>text/css<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token style\"><span class=\"token language-css\">\n        <span class=\"token selector\">p</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">&#123;</span>\n            <span class=\"token property\">font-weight</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> normal\n        <span class=\"token punctuation\">&#125;</span>\n\n        <span class=\"token comment\">/* 等于400 */</span>\n        <span class=\"token selector\">h1</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">&#123;</span>\n            <span class=\"token property\">font-weight</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 700\n        <span class=\"token punctuation\">&#125;</span>\n\n        <span class=\"token comment\">/* 等于bold */</span>\n        <span class=\"token selector\">div</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">&#123;</span>\n            <span class=\"token property\">font-weight</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> bolder\n        <span class=\"token punctuation\">&#125;</span>\n\n        <span class=\"token comment\">/* 可能为500 */</span>\n        <span class=\"token selector\">.bold</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">&#123;</span>\n            <span class=\"token comment\">/* 粗体样式类 */</span>\n            <span class=\"token property\">font-weight</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> bold<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n            <span class=\"token comment\">/* 加粗显示 */</span>\n        <span class=\"token punctuation\">&#125;</span>\n    </span></span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>style</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>head</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>body</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>p</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>绊爱（キズナアイ）是YouTube上一个虚拟YouTuber，自称为世界第一个Virtual YouTuber，YouTube频道名为A.I.Channel。角色形象由森倉円设计，3D模型由Tomitake制作，Tda监督。2016年12月25日，免费公开自身3D模型素材，作为圣诞礼物。2018年成为推广日本旅游的Come to Japan的宣传大使，目前是Kizuna AI株式会社的虚拟YouTuber和音乐艺术家。声称是人工智能（AI）。\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>p</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>body</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>html</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre>\n<h3 id=\"字体倾斜\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#字体倾斜\"></a> 字体倾斜</h3>\n<p><s>这个属性最常用于把倾斜的字体变得不倾斜</s></p>\n<p>使用font-style属性对元素的文字粗细定义样式，属性值为normal、italic、oblique。</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-html\" data-language=\"html\"><code class=\"language-html\"><span class=\"token doctype\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;!</span><span class=\"token doctype-tag\">doctype</span> <span class=\"token name\">html</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>html</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>head</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>meta</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">charset</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>utf-8<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>title</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>字体样式<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>title</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>style</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">type</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>text/css<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token style\"><span class=\"token language-css\">\n        <span class=\"token selector\">span</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">&#123;</span>\n            <span class=\"token property\">font-style</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> normal<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n        <span class=\"token punctuation\">&#125;</span>\n    </span></span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>style</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>head</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>body</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>p</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>i</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>绊爱（キズナアイ）是<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>span</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>YouTuber<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>span</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>上一个虚拟<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>span</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>YouTuber<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>span</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>，自称为世界第一个<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>span</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>YouTuber<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>span</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>，<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>span</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>YouTuber<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>span</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>频道名为A.I.Channel。角色形象由森倉円设计，3D模型由Tomitake制作，Tda监督。2016年12月25日，免费公开自身3D模型素材，作为圣诞礼物[1]。2018年成为推广日本旅游的Come\n            to Japan的宣传大使，目前是Kizuna AI株式会社的虚拟<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>span</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>YouTuber<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>span</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>和音乐艺术家。声称是人工智能（AI）。 <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>i</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>p</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>body</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n<span class=\"token comment\">&lt;!-- 所有的YouTuber都归正了。 --></span>\n\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>html</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre>\n<h3 id=\"行间距\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#行间距\"></a> 行间距</h3>\n<p>使用line-height属性对元素的文字行间距定义样式。</p>\n<p>常用单位px。</p>\n<h3 id=\"字体复合属性\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#字体复合属性\"></a> 字体复合属性</h3>\n<p>使用font属性对字体设置样式。<br />\n语法：<br />\nfont: font-style | font-variant | font-weight | font-size | line-height | font-family<br />\n属性值之间用空格分隔。至少设置字体大小和字体类型，且必须放在后面。各个属性值要严格遵循相应的顺序。</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-html\" data-language=\"html\"><code class=\"language-html\"><span class=\"token doctype\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;!</span><span class=\"token doctype-tag\">doctype</span> <span class=\"token name\">html</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>html</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>head</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>meta</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">charset</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>utf-8<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>title</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>字体样式<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>title</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>style</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">type</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>text/css<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token style\"><span class=\"token language-css\">\n        <span class=\"token selector\">body</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">&#123;</span>\n            <span class=\"token comment\">/* 斜体样式类 */</span>\n            <span class=\"token property\">font</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> bolder 24px <span class=\"token string\">\"隶书\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n            <span class=\"token comment\">/* 斜体 */</span>\n        <span class=\"token punctuation\">&#125;</span>\n    </span></span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>style</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>head</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>body</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>p</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>绊爱（キズナアイ）是YouTuber上一个虚拟YouTuber，自称为世界第一个YouTuber，YouTuber频道名为A.I.Channel。目前是Kizuna\n        AI株式会社的虚拟YouTuber和音乐艺术家。声称是人工智能（AI）。<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>p</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>body</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>html</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre>\n<h3 id=\"字体颜色\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#字体颜色\"></a> 字体颜色</h3>\n<p>使用color属性对元素的文字颜色定义样式。</p>\n<p>可以使用预定义的颜色、十六进制颜色、RGB表示颜色。</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-html\" data-language=\"html\"><code class=\"language-html\"><span class=\"token doctype\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;!</span><span class=\"token doctype-tag\">doctype</span> <span class=\"token name\">html</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>html</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>head</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>meta</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">charset</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>utf-8<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>title</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>字体样式<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>title</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>style</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">type</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>text/css<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token style\"><span class=\"token language-css\">\n        <span class=\"token selector\">body</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">&#123;</span>\n            <span class=\"token property\">color</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> gray<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n        <span class=\"token punctuation\">&#125;</span>\n\n        <span class=\"token selector\">p</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">&#123;</span>\n            <span class=\"token property\">color</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> #666666<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n        <span class=\"token punctuation\">&#125;</span>\n\n        <span class=\"token selector\">div</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">&#123;</span>\n            <span class=\"token property\">color</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token function\">rgb</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>120<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> 120<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> 120<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n        <span class=\"token punctuation\">&#125;</span>\n\n        <span class=\"token selector\">span</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">&#123;</span>\n            <span class=\"token property\">color</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token function\">rgb</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>50%<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> 50%<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> 50%<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n        <span class=\"token punctuation\">&#125;</span>\n    </span></span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>style</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>head</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>body</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>p</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>定义字体颜色<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>p</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>body</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>html</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre>\n<h3 id=\"文本对齐\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#文本对齐\"></a> 文本对齐</h3>\n<p>使用text-align属性对元素的对齐定义样式。<br />\n常用属性值有:left、right、center、justify、start、end、match-parent、justify-all。</p>\n<p>使用vertical-align属性对元素的垂直对齐定义样式。<br />\n常用属性有：auto、baseline、sub、super、top、text-top、middle、bottom、text-bottom、length。</p>\n<h3 id=\"文本装饰\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#文本装饰\"></a> 文本装饰</h3>\n<p>使用text-decoration属性定义字体的下划线效果。<br />\n常用属性有：none、underline、blink、overline、line-through。</p>\n<h3 id=\"文本缩进\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#文本缩进\"></a> 文本缩进</h3>\n<p>使用text-indent属性对元素的缩进定义样式,可以是浮点数，可以是负数。<br />\n常用单位是：em(字距)。</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-html\" data-language=\"html\"><code class=\"language-html\"><span class=\"token doctype\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;!</span><span class=\"token doctype-tag\">doctype</span> <span class=\"token name\">html</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>html</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>head</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>meta</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">charset</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>utf-8<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>title</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>文本样式<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>title</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>style</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">type</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>text/css<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token style\"><span class=\"token language-css\">\n        <span class=\"token selector\">p</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">&#123;</span>\n            <span class=\"token property\">text-indent</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> -2em<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n            <span class=\"token property\">padding-left</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 2em<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span><span class=\"token comment\">/* 左侧补白 */</span>\n        <span class=\"token punctuation\">&#125;</span>\n    </span></span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>style</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>head</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>body</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>h1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>《人间词话》节选<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>h1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>h2</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>王国维<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>h2</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>p</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>古今之成大事业、大学问者，必经过三种之境界：\"昨夜西风凋碧树。独上高楼，望断天涯路。\"此第一境也。\"衣带渐宽终不悔，为伊消得人憔悴。\"此第二境也。\"众里寻他千百度，蓦然回首，那人却在灯火阑珊处。\"此第三境也。此等语皆非大词人不能道。然遽以此意解释诸词，恐为晏欧诸公所不许也。\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>p</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>body</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>html</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre>\n","feature":true,"text":"上一篇学习了CSS的选择器，这一篇就学习： CSS属性 字体 使用font-family属性对元素的字体定义样式，可以设置多种不同的字体(如果浏览器不支持当前字体则找下一个字体替换)，字体之间用逗号隔开。字体名称可以是中文名，但是最好写英文名。 &lt;!doctype html...","link":"","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":"4.8k","symbolsTime":"4 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"前端","slug":"前端","count":6,"path":"api/categories/前端.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"CSS","slug":"CSS","count":4,"path":"api/tags/CSS.json"}],"toc":"<ol class=\"toc\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#css%E5%B1%9E%E6%80%A7\"><span class=\"toc-text\"> CSS属性</span></a><ol class=\"toc-child\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E5%AD%97%E4%BD%93\"><span class=\"toc-text\"> 字体</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E5%AD%97%E5%8F%B7\"><span class=\"toc-text\"> 字号</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E5%AD%97%E4%BD%93%E7%B2%97%E7%BB%86\"><span class=\"toc-text\"> 字体粗细</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E5%AD%97%E4%BD%93%E5%80%BE%E6%96%9C\"><span class=\"toc-text\"> 字体倾斜</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E8%A1%8C%E9%97%B4%E8%B7%9D\"><span class=\"toc-text\"> 行间距</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E5%AD%97%E4%BD%93%E5%A4%8D%E5%90%88%E5%B1%9E%E6%80%A7\"><span class=\"toc-text\"> 字体复合属性</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E5%AD%97%E4%BD%93%E9%A2%9C%E8%89%B2\"><span class=\"toc-text\"> 字体颜色</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E6%96%87%E6%9C%AC%E5%AF%B9%E9%BD%90\"><span class=\"toc-text\"> 文本对齐</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E6%96%87%E6%9C%AC%E8%A3%85%E9%A5%B0\"><span class=\"toc-text\"> 文本装饰</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E6%96%87%E6%9C%AC%E7%BC